cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.SY

This paper discusses the application of reinforcement learning (RL) algorithms for autonomous cyber defence in software-defined networking (SDN). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also focuses on the use of machine learning algorithms, specifically RL, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, since the application is in SDN, it could belong to cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Finally, since the paper discusses the use of RL agents, it could also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
